Indexer definitions: attribution and license
=============================================

The YAML files in this directory are Cardigann indexer definitions vendored,
unmodified, from the Prowlarr/Indexers project:

    https://github.com/Prowlarr/Indexers

They are licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 3.0 (GPL-3.0),
the same license as Prowlarr. minch-cli bundles only the `type: public`
definitions that its scoped Cardigann interpreter can run (no login/auth).

minch-cli does not alter the contents of these definitions; the
`npm run sync:definitions` script only downloads and filters them.

All credit for these definitions, and for the Cardigann definition format, goes
to the Prowlarr team and contributors.

A copy of the GPL-3.0 license text is available at:

    https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt
